= Wenqi Fan - Openings (Year-round Recruitment)

I am a Research Assistant Professor of the Department of Computing (COMP), The Hong Kong Polytechnic University (PolyU). 

Our research group are actively recruiting self-motivated *Postdoc, Ph.D. students, [https://www.polyu.edu.hk/comp/study/research-postgraduate-programme/joint-phd/ Joint PhD students], MPhil/Msc, and Research Assistants*, etc. 
Visiting scholars, interns, and self-funded students are also welcome. 
Send me an email if you are interested. 


 
